# 本地测试用的灵宠/字体素材:绝不进公开仓 / 不部署(只保留 README 文档)
# 你可在本地往这些目录丢任意素材自行测试,git 永远不会提交它们。
frontend-v4/world/sprites/spirits/*
!frontend-v4/world/sprites/spirits/README.md
# 例外:随行宠物 Tuxemon 像素素材(CC BY-SA 4.0,合规,随产品发布)
!frontend-v4/world/sprites/spirits/puff.png
!frontend-v4/world/sprites/spirits/ember.png
!frontend-v4/world/sprites/spirits/ripple.png
!frontend-v4/world/sprites/spirits/moss.png
!frontend-v4/world/sprites/spirits/breeze.png
!frontend-v4/world/sprites/spirits/pebble.png
!frontend-v4/world/sprites/spirits/glimmer.png
!frontend-v4/world/sprites/spirits/ATTRIBUTION.md
!frontend-v4/world/sprites/spirits/LICENSE-CC-BY-SA-4.0.txt
frontend-v4/world/fonts/*
!frontend-v4/world/fonts/README.md
# 例外:自托管的开放许可(OFL-1.1)像素中文字体 Fusion Pixel —— 合规,随产品发布
!frontend-v4/world/fonts/pixel.woff2
!frontend-v4/world/fonts/pixel.OFL.txt
living-oc/public/sprites/spirits/*
!living-oc/public/sprites/spirits/README.md
# 例外:随行宠物 Tuxemon 像素素材(CC BY-SA 4.0,合规,随产品发布)
!living-oc/public/sprites/spirits/puff.png
!living-oc/public/sprites/spirits/ember.png
!living-oc/public/sprites/spirits/ripple.png
!living-oc/public/sprites/spirits/moss.png
!living-oc/public/sprites/spirits/breeze.png
!living-oc/public/sprites/spirits/pebble.png
!living-oc/public/sprites/spirits/glimmer.png
!living-oc/public/sprites/spirits/ATTRIBUTION.md
!living-oc/public/sprites/spirits/LICENSE-CC-BY-SA-4.0.txt
living-oc/public/fonts/*
